data.description:
Southern Charm in highly sought-after Riverwalk! This 3-bed, 2.5-bath home welcomes you with its inviting front porch, perfect for your morning coffee.  Enjoy an open and airy floor plan with 10ft ceilings, custom plantation shutters, and elegant crown molding throughout the first floor, set the stage for a cozy and inviting atmosphere, accentuated by a beautiful gas fireplace.

The gourmet kitchen is ideal for entertaining, with stainless steel appliances, a gas cooktop, stunning white quartz countertops, and a large kitchen island.

Upstairs has 3 bedrooms, highlighted by a bright, spacious primary bedroom and bath. 

The true gem of this home is the back patio, with a pergola and a tranquil water feature and pond. The homeowner's custom landscaping and outdoor spaces make this a one-of-a-kind!

The vibrant, growing riverfront community features river access, unique dining and entertainment options, and more!  A must-see! Don't miss this exceptional property and community!
